msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda berada di luar AS, kami merekomendasikan NOWPayments (biaya "
"terendah, langsung ke dompet Anda). Jika Anda berada di AS, Stripe Crypto "
"juga merupakan opsi. Anda dapat mengaktifkan beberapa layanan dan membiarkan"
" pengunjung Anda memilih!"

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Metode Pembayaran Aktif"

msgid ""
