"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments memungkinkan Anda menerima pembayaran kartu kredit langsung ke "
"dompet kripto Anda. Dana langsung masuk ke dompet Anda – tanpa perantara."

