msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran Crypto Stripe (USDC) HANYA tersedia untuk bisnis yang berbasis di"
" AS. Jika Anda berada di luar AS, Stripe hanya akan menerima pembayaran "
"kartu kredit ke saldo Stripe Anda (bukan langsung ke crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda berada di AS, Anda dapat menggunakan Stripe untuk menerima crypto "
"secara langsung. Jika berada di luar, pertimbangkan NOWPayments atau "
"CoinGate untuk pembayaran crypto langsung."

